# hocusfocus:1.7.0


```bash
npm i -g emrahburak/hocusfocus
or
git clone https://github.com/emrahburak/hocusfocus.git
cd /hocusfocus
npm link
or 
npm i -g .
```

```bash
hocusfocus
or
hocusfocus -t 1500
or
hocusfocus --time 15m
or
hocusfocus -t 2h10m -p %your-music-file-path-for-alternatives-beep-sound%
```



